high_descs: Move to the stove to the right of the sink
Pick up a pan from the stove
Move to the fridge behind you
Chill the pan in the fridge for a moment
Move to the cabinet to the right of the fridge
Put the pan in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk through the kitchen over to the stove
Pick up the pan from the back left stove burner
Turn around and walk over to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge then remove it
Turn around, walk a few feet, then turn back to face toward the counter just right of the fridge
Open the lower cabinet right of the fridge and put the pan in it
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the counter, then turn to the right and go to the stove.
Pick up the skillet that is on the back left stove burner.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the skillet inside the fridge and close the door, take the skillet out of the fridge.
Go to the cabinet that is on the right of the fridge underneath the microwave.
Put the skillet inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold skillet in a cabinet.
